WEBVTT

00:00.136 --> 00:03.005
I'm engaged.
To miss Mary Lockwood.

00:03.007 --> 00:04.973
Grindle kept
a ledger, listed every woman

00:04.975 --> 00:06.475
who needed her service and
every man who paid for it.

00:06.477 --> 00:07.643
How much?

00:07.645 --> 00:08.844
Where is Annie?

00:08.846 --> 00:11.113
I sent her away

00:11.115 --> 00:12.981
to live with a family
in California.

00:12.983 --> 00:14.249
Hello, girl.

00:14.251 --> 00:16.117
He's not my father.

00:16.120 --> 00:18.287
I'll behave!
Please! No!

